                            Id = 8,
                            Description = @"If you’re thirsting for danger and lusting for loot, then I have just the game for you! Grab your friends, hone your blades and set off for adventure in the free to play Sandbox MMORPG Trove. Developed and published by Trion Worlds, Trove is the story of The Sun Goddess, who has shattered the world into infinite realms. You’re job is to explore build and protect those realms, all in the name of fun!

