                            Description = @"Dragon Saga is a free to play arcade­-style side­-scrolling 3D MMORPG developed and published by Gravity Interactive. In the world of Dragon Saga, you will choose your character from one of six classes ­ Warrior, Mage, Thief, Archer, Shaman or Twin Fighter, and explore a rich world filled with unique monsters. As you progress, you’ll be able to power up and unlock devastating abilities, hidden combos and hilarious skill effects. As you customize your character, those six classes expand into 30 different classes, allowing for nearly unlimited character customization.

